    "If I # T is a flat chain, then so is T.Proof.",
    "Let F: R m → R d be given by F = I -1 • P, where P is the orthonormal projection to I(R d).",
    "Then one may verify that F # I # T = T. Therefore, if I # T is a flat chain, then by the discussion above, also T = F # I # T is a flat chain.",
